import resume from '../assets/pdf/resume.pdf'

export const headerData = {
    name: 'Satkirti Mishra',
    title: "Web Developer",
    desciption:"I am a recent graduate with a Bachelor's degree in Information Technology. Throughout my academic career, I have gained expertise in languages such as C, C++, and Python, and I have also learned web development skills such as HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. I have also completed an internship at Microsoft where I worked on a live project related to facial recognition. In my free time, I enjoy solving coding problems on platforms like Leetcode and GeeksforGeeks. I am excited to apply my technical skills and knowledge to contribute to a team and learn new things in a professional setting.",
    resumePdf: resume
}
